overview: 3.0 continues their upgrade as they face UltraMantis Black and Crossbones! Vin Gerard harbors a grudge against Jigsaw. Eddie Kingston sends Claudio Castagnoli a message when he fights Lince Dorado, then makes his presence known when Mike Quackenbush, Hallowicked and Frightmare take on the BDK!
title: CHIKARA Testimony Of Evil
